General.Name: Westar Resources Ltd
General.Description: Westar Resources Limited, together with its subsidiaries, explores for and develops mineral properties in Western Australia. It primarily explores for gold and base metal deposits. The company holds interests in the Sandstone projects located to the northeast of Perth and north-northwest of Kalgoorlie; and Mount Magnet projects located in the Murchison Mineral Field proximal to the historical mining center of Mount Magnet. It also holds interests in the Pilbara project located in the Pilbara; and Southern Cross projects in Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2019 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
